result.formatted_address: 18 Chun Yin Square, Yuen Long, Hong Kong
result.name: 海椰中西美食坊

reviews.text:
The joint is a bit cramped, with tables really close together. But hey, this is Hong Kong! 

I had lunch here & price is a bargain. HKD38 with both soup & coffee/tea included. I ordered minced beef rice with ham & egg. Sauce is a pleasant surprise. 

Tea is so so. Do not have high expectation. 😏

Hygiene is not bad for a place in Yuen Long. Hey, this is not Yoho Mall after all. 😁
Average Yuan Long price, taste is OK, soup is a bit salty. Place is clean tho.
食品選擇多，價錢大衆化。但味道一般，座位亦較窄。
味道唔錯，價錢便宜，比一般茶餐廳好
叫左海南雞飯，牛排餐，兩個都唔掂，唔正中既海南雞飯加埋幾劣質既牛排。如果個牛排唔適合做5成熟，應該通知顧客先或者就唔好問顧客要幾成熟了，免得肉中間切開仲好似仲雪藏緊咁樣。
